ant, DVD recorders are your best choice. Instead of leaving your favorite movies on VHS cassettes that slowly degrade, you can copy your taped movies to DVDs. Your movies will last longer and you won t have to worry about repair and compatibility issues as VCRs become less and less prevalent. You ll also save money using DVDs over VHS cassettes.","No  matter what you are using the DVD recorder for, it s a great way to get reliable entertainment that you can view again and again.","In this site, you&#39;ll find <a href=\"/electronics\">articles on buying DVD recorders</a>, news stories and comprehensive reviews on DVD recorders that will help you make an informed decision on which one is right for you. At TopTenREVIEWS We Do the Research So You Don t Have To. ","<strong>DVD Recorders:  What to Look For</strong>","Not all DVD recorders are created equal. You want to get a reliable product that does quality recordings. We took all this and more into account when ranking DVD recorders. We used a variety of criteria to do the ranking, and below you ll find an explanation of some of the most important considerations in choosing the top DVD recorders.","<strong>Outputs</strong><br/>This is the kinds of formats that the DVD recorder can burn onto the DVD. Make sure that your DVD recorder can use formats that are compatible with your DVD player and any other devices in your home entertainment center.","<strong>Hard Drive Capacity<br/></strong>Having a good hard drive can be useful if you want to store or edit video before you burn it to a disc. In this category, more is better.","<strong>DVD Record Time<br/></strong>It s important to have a DVD recorder that can record for long periods of time, especially if you have a large video or a long TV show to record. The longer the DVD record time, the longer you can capture video.","<strong>TV Tuner</strong><br/>If you want to record anything from your TV, like your favorite shows or an important game, then you need to make sure your DVD recorder has a TV tuner.","With all this information, you can make an informed decision about which DVD recorder is best for you. To get a breakdown of all the features and criteria for each product, take a look at our side-by-side comparison of <strong>DVD recorders</strong>. Be sure to check out our top rated products, the <a href=\"/electronics/home-entertainment/best-dvd-recorder-players/toshiba-dr420-review/\">Toshiba DR430</a>, <a href=\"/electronics/home-entertainment/best-dvd-recorder-players/toshiba-dr410-22967-review/\">Toshiba D-R410</a> and <a href=\"/electronics/home-entertainment/best-dvd-recorder-players/panasonic-dmr-ez28k-22966-review/\">Panasonic DMR EZ28K</a>."]},"id":"bd111ad7-17a9-4c09-87bc-3431aef2293a","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Related Product Reviews"},"id":"53ba4fcb-1b44-4a36-9687-265f0b9303b0","type":"heading"},{"data":{"items":["<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0038JECKY/?&tag=ttr_dvdrecorder_dvdplayers-20&ascsubtag=[site|ttr[cat|265[art|NA[pid|48548[tid|NA[bbc|NA\">Toshiba DR430</a>","<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0014176XI/?&tag=ttr_dvdrecorder_dvdplayers-20&ascsubtag=[site|ttr[cat|265[art|NA[pid|25793[tid|NA[bbc|NA\">Toshiba D-R410</a>","<a href=\"http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=Cty0dj6o3sg&offerid=101744.4227188&type=15&subid=0\">Panasonic DMR EZ28K</a>","<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B001I59HSW/?&tag=ttr_dvdrecorder_dvdplayers-20&ascsubtag=[site|ttr[cat|265[art|NA[pid|48547[tid|NA[bbc|NA\">Sony RDR-GX257</a>","<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0023ZLBDA/?&tag=ttr_dvdrecorder_dvdplayers-20&ascsubtag=[site|ttr[cat|265[art|NA[pid|48551[tid|NA[bbc|NA\">Toshiba DKR40</a>","<a href=\"http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=Cty0dj6o3sg&offerid=101744.4227189&type=15&subid=0\">Panasonic Diga DMR-EZ48VK</a>","<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B000F4C2AM/?&tag=ttr_dvdrecorder_dvdplayers-20&ascsubtag=[site|ttr[cat|265[art|NA[pid|6299[tid|NA[bbc|NA\">Panasonic